data.description: Centrally located beautiful home on city water and sewer. Corner lot. Open floor plan with attached dining room, 3 bedrooms with den, 2 bath, and 2 car garage. Beautiful back yard with plenty of room for a pool. Lot behind home with separate deed is included in the purchase price. Kitchen has granite countertops, stainless steal appliances, and soft close drawers and cabinets. Cozy floorplan. Tile throughout the home. Hurricane shutters. The master bedroom has a spacious bathroom that contains separate shower & tub, convenient access linen closet, dual sink and Walk-in closets. Come see it and you will fall in love with this property.
